ty, and central surface brightness as\nthe Local Group dwarfs do, and appear to be subject to morphological\nsegregation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 Jul 2001 20:31:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2007-05-23"}
